TEXT(beginproblem());


##############################################################
#
#  Setup
#
#

Context("Numeric");
#given
$t = random(10, 50, 10);


#computation
$d = 0.5*$t*(0.5*$t);


$imagescale = 0.2;
$width = $imagescale*2135;
$height = $imagescale*2732;
#set tolerance
Context()->flags->set(
tolerance=>.05,
tolType=>'relative');

##############################################################
#
#  PGML 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

[@ image( "21-P-KM-GD-007.png", width=>[0], height=>[0]) @]*

A car is accelerating, and its velocity is shown in the graph above.

What is the distance travelled by the car at time [`t =`] [`[$t]`] seconds?

[`d = `] [_____]{"$d"} [`m`]

END_PGML

